snippet.title: Throw Anything Playstation VR
snippet.description:
Finally , a more fun, enhanced 'Throw Anything' is coming out on the PlayStation VR
'Throw Anything' will be released on February 6, 2020
I'm so sorry. The launch date has been changed from January 30 to February 6.

 #PS VR #Playstation VR #Throw Anything #Weird zombie
